    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你被绑架后在地下室醒来。在寻找逃生方法的过程中，你发现这里最近发生了一件可怕的事情。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>找到逃生的办法。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索地下室，寻找逃生的出口。但某些东西会试图把你留在里面。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285930/extras/9e181208dd55ce9b2402ac1e87e4f0cf.poster.avif?t=1747051322\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285930/extras/9e181208dd55ce9b2402ac1e87e4f0cf.webm?t=1747051322\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285930/extras/9e181208dd55ce9b2402ac1e87e4f0cf.mp4?t=1747051322\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>你并不孤单。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有什么东西总是在附近，如果你看到它，找个地方躲起来或逃跑以求生存。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285930/extras/f09df9095945cca157cd4e083c1eac54.poster.avif?t=1747051322\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285930/extras/f09df9095945cca157cd4e083c1eac54.webm?t=1747051322\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285930/extras/f09df9095945cca157cd4e083c1eac54.mp4?t=1747051322\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>秘密和谜题。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解开谜题，发现秘密，拼凑出这里发生的故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285930/extras/e38ae12b11875de693884352eb39b736.poster.avif?t=1747051322\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285930/extras/e38ae12b11875de693884352eb39b736.webm?t=1747051322\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285930/extras/e38ae12b11875de693884352eb39b736.mp4?t=1747051322\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>特点。</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >两个主要结局和一个秘密结局。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >预计游戏时长：20-40分钟。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >谜题。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主要是一款第一人称步行模拟游戏。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
